Uses of Package
org.jvault.metadata

  • Packages that use org.jvault.metadata 
    Package Description
    org.jvault.annotation
    Meta-information of Jvault about register beans, inject beans
    org.jvault.bean
    Package containing information related to Bean.
    org.jvault.bean.composition
    Package containing implementations of bean interfaces.
    org.jvault.beanloader
    Packages that load Bean
    org.jvault.extension
    A package that helps to extend Jvault API on Runtime.
    org.jvault.factory
    Package with JvaultFactory for creating Jvaults.
    org.jvault.factory.buildinfo
    Package that parameter of the JvaultFactory for build Vault and Bean.
    org.jvault.factory.buildinfo.extensible
    Extension point of VaultFactoryBuildInfo behavior.
    org.jvault.factory.extensible
    Extension point of VaultFactory behavior.
    org.jvault.factory.storage  
    org.jvault.util
    Packages that support Jvault API globally.
    org.jvault.vault
    Packages containing Vault that manage generated Bean and inject it into user class.
